<concept id="concept_uninstall"
                            xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Uninstallation</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>The uninstallation of <ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> and its OpenStack extensions comprises the following steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>Uninstalling a Metrics Agent from an OpenStack node.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Uninstalling a Log Agent from an OpenStack node.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Uninstalling the Horizon Plugin from the node where the OpenStack Horizon service is deployed.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Uninstalling the Monitoring Service.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Removing the projects, users, and roles prepared for the OpenStack integration.</p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
